VoiceEars
/* MainActivity */ Speak Type a message scroll down Speak
Start speaking or type and click Speak button. Click the face icon at top-right to toggle the gender. Enter the subscription key and region to start using this app. Failed to authenticate. Check the API key and region. Allow this app to record your audio to enable Speech-to-text. WARNING: Speech-to-text is disabled. To enable it, go to Settings and allow this app to access your microphone and restart the app.
/* Main Menu */ Settings
/* SettingsActivity */ Azure Cognitive Services API Key: api key Region: region Create a Cognitive Services service in Azure Portal and go to Resource Management > Keys to get your subscription key. SAVE
